[Student "S"]
{The bidding has been as shown.   

Your best suit is \Hs. But partner didn't ask you to bid \Hs, he asked you to pick a Minor. You know you will have an 8-card fit in \Ds so you take the safe approach and bid 3\D. Everybody passes.}

